              </p>
              <me>
                DS_3 = \{0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, .5, 1\}\quad .
              </me>
              <p>
                Finally, find the range<idx>range</idx>,
                <m>IQR</m><idx><m>IQR</m>, inter-quartile range</idx>, and standard
